      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON IRAOLA (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (16.33) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Top prospect. MADE IN LONDON (2) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at Taree Super Track finishing 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (17.55). Has placed a couple of times at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. Leading chance. SKINNY MARIE (8) is better than last start when fifth (23.26) from Box 5 at this track over 400m. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Has the ability to give this a shake. BELTONE BOY (4) was strongly fancied last time but ran below expectations when fourth (23.13), beaten 4.5 lengths. Form from his last run is proving to be solid.",
